              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "**Answer the following questions according to the text.**\na. Which aspects does the Triple Bottom Line concept refer to?\nb. Does the speaker intend to apply the new concept in the management of his company? Justify.\nc. Why is it easier to highlight successes than failures?"
            },
            {
              "id": "v1_p1_a_3_solution_2",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "a. It refers to social, environmental and financial aspects/ people, planet and profits.\nb. Yes, because for him it is necessary to walk the talk and translate the concept into the reality of running a business such as ours.\nc. Because it's hard to be honest and self critical in a public way."
